nathaniel [ a.t ] rogers.com

Story:
Pretty basic stuff here, once the round starts the guns fall, and it will be raining men.. er... lead. The last team member(s) standing wins.

The cathedral ceiling and two walkways on the wall is great for low-gravity servers. 

*36 total spawn points, 18 Terrorist, 18 Counter-Terrorist.
*36 M4A1s', 30 rounds each.
*1 Custom texture.
